**Yet still shine with hope stronger than any medicine.**  

**Every donation - every act of kindness -**  
**Is another chance at childhood, another reason to smile,**  
**Another step toward hearing "cancer-free."**  

**Join us in turning their struggles into victories,**  
**Because every child deserves to dream in color,**  
**To laugh without pain,**  
**To simply be a kid.**  

